i		gopher.black	70
iCodes of Conduct attempt to accomplish a GOOD. They attempt to		gopher.black	70
iensure that individuals are not exposed to unfair prejudice. This		gopher.black	70
iis a movement toward equality, which it itself is also a GOOD. (I		gopher.black	70
