i		gopher.black	70
iCodes of Conduct are also weapons. They are wielded by the		gopher.black	70
ioppressed and marginalized with a powerful blow aimed at those		gopher.black	70
ithey feel have transgressed. Is this a GOOD? Providing		gopher.black	70
ia reciprocal power dynamic is an expression of vengeance, not of		gopher.black	70
ijustice. It does not guarantee liberty or equality. It guarantees		gopher.black	70
ia shifted power-base and a new set of mores to be navigated, or		gopher.black	70
ielse. This is not good. This is bad.		gopher.black	70
